Package: AquaMicrobiomeIndicators
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Indicator Species Analysis for Aquatic Microbiome Assessment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Luciana", "Griffero",
           email = "lugrif@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for adaptive indicator species analysis in aquatic 
    microbiome datasets. The package integrates flexible threshold selection 
    for fidelity (A), specificity (B), and sqrtIV pruning, along with coverage 
    estimation to support ecological status assessment across environmental 
    gradients.
